Here are links to information relating **data-management** with **tidy-data** and R's suite of packages called **tidyverse**

Ross, Z. et. al. Declutter your workflow with tidy tools. PeerJ Preprints
https://peerj.com/preprints/3180/

Wickham. H. 2014. Tidy Data.
http://vita.had.co.nz/papers/tidy-data.pdf

Garrett Grolemund and Hadley Wickham. R for data science. Online book.
http://r4ds.had.co.nz/

McNamara. A. & Horton. N.J. 2017. Wrangling categorical data in R.
https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/00031305.2017.1356375

